# For PCBs designed using KiCad: https://www.kicad.org/
# Format documentation: https://kicad.org/help/file-formats/


# Kibot
kibot_errors.filter
*-drc.txt
*-drc.html

# Freerouting
freerouting/freerouting-*.jar
freerouting/freerouting.log

# Temporary files
*.000
*.bak
*.bck
*.kicad_pcb-bak
*.kicad_sch-bak
*-backups
*-backups/*
*.sch-bak
*~
_autosave-*
*.tmp
*-save.pro
*-save.kicad_pcb
fp-info-cache
*.lck
logs


# Exported BOM files
*.xml
!log4j2.xml
*.csv
# --- SlimSplaydy production layout (see production-panel/README.md) ---
# Fabrication Toolkit scratch output; the canonical order set is /production-panel/
panel/production/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
# ...but DO track the canonical JLC order CSVs (overrides the global *.csv rule above)
!production-panel/positions.csv
!production-panel/bom.csv
